SeaborgiumSea_Script1:
    lock
    faceplayer
    msgbox SeaborgiumSea_Script1_Text
    release
    end

SeaborgiumSea_Script1_Text:
    .string "Wow, you really need a Pok{EACUTE}mon\n"
    .string "to swim for you?\p"
    .string "I would just learn to swim by myself,\n"
    .string "but maybe I'm weird.$"

SeaborgiumSea_Script2:
    lock
    faceplayer
    msgbox SeaborgiumSea_Script2_Text
    release
    end

SeaborgiumSea_Script2_Text:
    .string "The library in Southern Glitchland\n"
    .string "has books on pretty much any topic.\p"
    .string "For instance, I recently read the\n"
    .string "book {LQUOT}Green Bacon and Eggs{RQUOT}.\p"
    .string "It's great! It answered all my questions\n"
    .string "about coelacanth paleobiology.$"

SeaborgiumSea_Script3:
    lock
    faceplayer
    msgbox SeaborgiumSea_Script3_Text
    release
    end

SeaborgiumSea_Script3_Text:
    .string "The merchant here sold me a beautiful\n"
    .string "NUGGET for just {DOLLAR}8000.\p"
    .string "I'm sure I'll be able to sell it for\n"
    .string "a lot more at a POK{EACUTE}MON MART!$"

SeaborgiumSea_Script4:
    lock
    faceplayer
    msgbox SeaborgiumSea_Script4_Text
    release
    end

SeaborgiumSea_Script4_Text:
    .string "The Seaborgium Sea is Glitchland's\n"
    .string "prime swimming and fishing spot.\p"
    .string "But the name just bothers me. It makes\n"
    .string "me want a VERY VERY VERY FLYING YAK.$"
